This video contains few words that may be offensive for few group of people it may be containing the words that create hatred between the people and yes it may let many people to judge by the illogical statements given by this man.

But I respect this person just because atleast he raised his voice to ask better persons such as Laure to uplift the Rap battles that was in good peak at that time. Well, Laure was never personally liable to do what other people want coz its a matter of freedom, but people who expected much more better from him were badly broken down. I think No-one can deny that he somewhere left the journey of uplifting the Raw Bars in the middle and this was actually realised by Sacar that he, the Laure can Lead the dream that YB had actually imagined for the whole NEPHOP.

But people like us are meant to pull legs of people rather to support the voices raised, actually for the betterment of people, as a whole. Yes the way Sacar raised his voice was kind if shameful but did anyone tried raising voice for that growing NEPHOP in the way they think was better? I don‚Äôt think so. I am sorry if I misleaded some people or if I did sth wrong that actually hurts your feelings but i too expected much more support for the whole people, in NEPHOP combinely, from Laure daju. I too had expected the leadership in him and he could actually lead the NEPHOP that would uplift the whole NEPHOP and would take it to a better height till date.
